title: Starting up a new 5s team, LF Mid and Top
body: Hi, I'm looking to start a new 5's team to play mostly Ranked 5's and maybe enter a few tourneys, so I'll be holding tryouts today from around 5 PM EST to 10 PM EST (the times we actually play will be closer to 7-11 unless everyone is on early). Please be at least Gold 5, no higher than Plat 3 for now. Leave your ign with na.op.gg link, champ pool, and summarize any experience you may have with 5s teams. Don't add me on the client, I'll lose track of you (I have way too many friends =P), I'll add you when tryouts are about to start.
